        <h4>In this type of task you have to design a room</h4>
        <h5>• Pull one of the things from above down in the building room.<br/>
• Doubble click on a thing, if you want to turn it around. You can also click on it by using the arrow keys to turn it.<br/>
• Pull things around in the building room, if they have to be placed differently.<br/>
• <span class="txt-underline">Some things can snap against each other, for example the ends without boards on two fields. In a room, a shelving unit snap at a wall. </span><br/>
• Zoom in and out by rolling the scroll wheel or your trackpad, while <img src="pil2.svg" alt="pil2" width="20" height="32"/> is in the building room<br/>
• Click on the two arrows at the bottom, if you want to turn the camera.<br/>
• Hold the left scroll wheel or trackpad down and move <img src="pil2.svg" alt="pil2" width="20" height="32"/> around, if you wish to move the camera.</h5>
        <h6>Try to build a mini golf court.</h6>
